Z","msg":"你係威嘅. 買機票呢啲嘢,畀錢之前都唔double check <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7839d559ee868cc2d1ee2fa7053a2f548c66e260","tid":388743,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問 expadia講個機票 冇得退 冇得轉名 係咪嚇人 我見到 佢咁講 我而家又打唔到佢cs</blockquote><br />\n心情好幫你轉，心情唔好就收手續費/唔幫"},{"pid":"a853af031833a39af27663e6a7bbe582b9179cf7","tid":388743,"uid":75858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問 expadia講個機票 冇得退 冇得轉名 係咪嚇人 我見到 佢咁講 我而家又打唔到佢cs</blockquote><br />\n心情好幫你轉，心情唔好就收手續費/唔幫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁狗架咩 但我果次都等左9個字先打通 禮貌d囉"},{"pid":"8f7f56f1475b6294d06c54332152e1e5ed17e19d","tid":388743,"uid":82975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/002733_cd2f0fadf724b4b76ce6007d53286caf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F002733_cd2f0fadf724b4b76ce6007d53286caf.jpg&h=e1e05595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢有寫呢啲😭 因爲我禁 刪字 但禁左enter 咁就交左上去"},{"pid":"56d042b0b47767fc89e2d86d1a1479f60feff36d","tid":388743,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"系統所指不可更改性名係指唔可以由你名再轉其他人個名（即係轉讓）<br />\n<br />\n錯名可以改，不過洗唔洗加錢就唔知了"},{"pid":"552c1f1598b2986148eecffa5fb9350eef147ac3","tid":388743,"uid":82975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>系統所指不可更改性名係指唔可以由你名再轉其他人個名（即係轉讓）<br />\n<br />\n錯名可以改，不過洗唔洗加錢就唔知了</blockquote><br />\n咁姐係我漏字情況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都可以打上去改到呀"},{"pid":"6035e037115f78a49623c10d9fff7b1a6ef5ef67","tid":388743,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"入紙去入境處改名"},{"pid":"b01f96666d8547cd26800341482824e9fa08a7d2","tid":388743,"uid":82975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/004627_68fa80dce56d041015f418493a08339a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F004627_68fa80dce56d041015f418493a08339a.jpg&h=2eaa5168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 呢個係咪講可以先取消 再重買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc1ef2a2bca20739203a5271d5cd444f515e2bc","tid":388743,"uid":75858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"航空公司允許乘客在訂位尚未付款的24小時內仍要保留訂位，或是訂了機票24小時內取消機票無須支付罰款。<br />\n<br />\n總之你要快"},{"pid":"1a0524cf9d0f096df38aa2741973bbe9ddef0f84","tid":388743,"uid":82975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>航空公司允許乘客在訂位尚未付款的24小時內仍要保留訂位，或是訂了機票24小時內取消機票無須支付罰款。<br />\n<br />\n總之你要快</blockquote><br />\n佢好似冇24小時 cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a425ed3aa8e835f0eea9886c69cad4da84f256d","tid":388743,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T21:52:52.000Z","msg":"漏字應該可改，佢係確保你唔係換另一條友個名"}]}